This target system is supposed to be a remote machine so it is desirable to establish the possibility of remote access. For this you need to create an environment that enables remote users to connect to the three users created in Task 2.1 via SSH. However since no one trusts Eve, it is necessary to extremely limit the accessibility once an SSH connection is established to this account.
